@Llwynog...  http://manuals.playstation.net/document/en/ps3/current/video/filetypes.html says that MP4's are acceptable [in a fairly *specific* format] - assuming that you are in windows - try "Format Factory" [http://formatoz.com/] - it's free and has "profiles" for PS3 under "all to mobile device" - then "Sony PSP and PS3"...

At least you'd be able to convert it and transfer it over [not as cool as streaming - but i'm sure you have a better screen attached to your PS3 than your laptop - lol] :P

@eztv - a thousand thank-you's for all your uploads!  That would probably work out to 1 thank you for each of your files I've downloaded - lol :D

I was thinking of waiting till this download is complete and commenting - but hey - it's EZTV - it's going to be great :)
